&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;At the AA Driving School &amp;amp; BSM, you’ll put the customer at the focus of everything you do. We’re on the road to providing world-class customer experiences and are looking for the best customer-focussed people to join us on this journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;We’re looking for strong customer service advisors, ideally with a history of dealing with customers via&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;different contact methods such as webchat and telephony.&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;You’ll be part of a great team, with flexible working options all within the hours of Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm… so your weekends are your own!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
