&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inbound &amp;amp; Outbound Contact Handling&lt;/strong&gt;: Manage inbound chats from our pupils, inbound calls from instructors or Motability pupils, and make outbound calls to any of these customer types as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Journey Management&lt;/strong&gt;: Assign instructors for Motability pupils, follow up on lesson progress, and support learners through to their driving test.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complaint Resolution &amp;amp; Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;: Resolve complaints at first contact across all channels, taking full ownership of queries and liaising with instructors or franchisees to ensure resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Admin &amp;amp; Financial Tasks&lt;/strong&gt;: Complete daily admin including emails, Motability reports, account setups, and handle payments and refunds accurately.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Service Excellence &amp;amp; Product Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;: Deliver high-quality service, promote self-serve options, stay informed on products, and maintain professionalism during busy periods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
