&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;*** C&#39;est ici que votre organisation peut créer une introduction cohérente à tous vos emplois, en créant une cohérence dans la voix et la messagerie dans tous les postes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be Better – Be part of not one, but two iconic brands.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Step into a role that blends cutting-edge technology with customer-first service. As a Roadside&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Dedicated Technician&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;The AA&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll represent the most respected names in motoring. This is more than a technician role—it&#39;s your chance to deliver a high-calibre experience that keeps customers moving with confidence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;This is the job&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;prestige roadside support&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;for vehicles, using manufacturer-specific tools and diagnostics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take complete ownership of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;customer experience&lt;/strong&gt;, from arrival to completion of the repair&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Combine technical skill with excellent communication to ensure customer satisfaction every time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle a mix of warranty work, roadside diagnostics, and advanced repairs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start and end your day at home with a fully equipped JLR van, tools, and uniform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work 40 hours/week – currently with a 7am–9pm shift range, with flexible standby hours to suit your life&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What will I be doing?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NVQ Level 3 (or equivalent) in Vehicle Maintenance &amp;amp; Repair&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confident, independent, and customer focused&lt;/li&gt;
