&lt;p&gt;Tietoevry is world leader in high expertise product development services and niche products for Automotive, Wireless and Cloud.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We develop software for the world’s most advanced global technology companies building 5G networks, IoT platforms, Connected &amp;amp; Autonomous Cars and Smart Devices. We’re a key partner to our customers, helping them bring fantastic and innovative products to market with success.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project&amp;nbsp;description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Full stack Android OS Developers willing to join our team and work closely with one of the world’s leading customers from automotive Tier 1 and SmartTV sector. You will be dealing with the most recent SW and HW on the market, touching the latest technologies in automotive industries, focusing on the modern automotive hypervisor-based solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role&amp;nbsp;description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The daily work will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring-up of new HW on Android Automotive/Android TV&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designing and developing Android Automotive/Android TV and Customer features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integration of Customer applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participation on Google certification process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communication with internal and external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in development in Android OS (TV, mobile or Automotive)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full stack Android OS SW development and integration, especially with deep experience in Linux and/or Android lower layers e.g. kernel, framework, vendor specific libraries, device drivers, protocols stacks&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of Android Architecture, Android Ecosystem and Android Debugging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Automotive projects (nice to have)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good analytical and communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent English&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
