&lt;h2 class=&quot;job-details__description-header text-color-secondary font-family-secondary&quot; data-bind=&quot;i18n: &#39;job-details.job-description-title&#39;&quot;&gt;Job Description -&amp;nbsp; THIS IS A DEMO ENVIRONMENT - Not a real job&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;job-details__description-content basic-formatter&quot; data-bind=&quot;html: pageData().job.description&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protect EMPLOYER’s data and the trust of millions worldwide who rely on it.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join EMPLOYER&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;as an application cybersecurity engineer and play a critical role in securing the applications and infrastructure that power data-driven decisions around the world. You’ll be a vital thought leader as you collaborate with developers and architects to embed security into every stage of the software development life cycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this hands-on role,&amp;nbsp;you will work&amp;nbsp;across teams — from data science to DevSecOps — to build secure systems from the ground up. You’ll use a modern tech stack and work with cloud-native infrastructure, containers, automation tools and CI/CD security integrations. You’ll also have the autonomy to innovate, the support to grow and the opportunity to make a lasting impact on a global scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
